Process called "linear_srgb_to_xyz_x" takes r as Float, g as Float, b as Float returns Float:
    @Reasoning
    Row 0 of the sRGB linear-RGB -> XYZ-D65 matrix.
    @End Reasoning
    @Implementation
    IEC 61966-2-1 coefficients (Bradford-adapted to D65).
    @End Implementation
    @Performance_Hints
    Three multiplies, two adds.
    @End Performance_Hints
    @Security_Scope
    Pure.
    @End Security_Scope
    Return ((0.4124564 multiplied by r) plus (0.3575761 multiplied by g)) plus (0.1804375 multiplied by b)
End Process

Process called "linear_srgb_to_xyz_y" takes r as Float, g as Float, b as Float returns Float:
